Name: Change Location of Soundbank

Scripts.Script:
D4886: [16, "Part 1 (DEFAULT: 0059)", hex]
D488E: [16, "Part 2 (DEFAULT: 3560)", hex]
D48A2: [copy, D4886, D4888]
D48A6: [copy, D488E, D4890]

//For XXXXXXXX, change the value to place you want the soundbank to go
XXXXXXXX: [copy, 593560, 7B0860]

Description:
Changes the soundbank location.
Default Location: 593560
